title: Divine Perspective
summary: Divine Perspective Manhua An accident gave Ye Han an amazing perspective ability. Since then, his life has become rich and colorful, pioneering the strongest business empire, dominating the world of gambling, rejuvenating with one-handed medical skills, and becoming a master of medical ethics. Sitting on billions of fortunes, Loli, Yujie, Jinghua, and the goddess rushed towards him. As a man, but also a limited edition man, Ye Han was under great pressure and had to explore with several grave robbers. Genius Mad Doctor Genius Mad Man 神级透视
